Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐～ 阿土 这周日一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 周日很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！周日忙什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 大人有很多事情要忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的事？难道说除了杏以外还有其他恋人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这样啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然阿土说他没有其他恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看他那个样子一定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来邀请我约会也一定是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师的话 这个可能性很低…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阿土很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是本人不去邀请别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有其他女人去主动邀请他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去调查他周日到底要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种工作的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查各种各样的事情的就是侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个 杏要当侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大体情况我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就靠你们几个没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 就在附近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我借走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题的话马上给妈妈打电话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸侦探团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 又回到原地了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡个回笼觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是土田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来是杏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么大清早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早上 已经中午了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的周日一整天都待在家里很浪费的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探居然给接下来要调查的人打电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 土田老师出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都待在家里很浪费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来要对阿土进行跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 开始跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸侦探团 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好像被人跟踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 有小猫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小杏快点跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是日向 诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫波的会不会出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拿到想要的不甘休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的一己之见…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他喜欢这样的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这边的是熊猫猫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100日元好贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅有100日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小杏 小梅 跟踪跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意不要跟丢了土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 杏会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好奇怪的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对幼稚园的孩子来说做侦探太勉强了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进家庭餐厅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是要等女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师笑得真灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是要等自己的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 阿土这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土这个笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等的人不来 心情还那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是看着女服务员 自己在一边偷乐而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！那边那个胸真大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被我猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身制服很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏完全不在乎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这总比有了别的恋人好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个偶像终于也下水啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看H书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H书…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是自然规律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视上说过的 健全的男性对这种东西很有兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 不会因为这种事就放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟他对视…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话跟你说 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有话说？我没什么要说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长说了 让你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不不不不 我不过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师好像被找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找茬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被可怕的坏人缠住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快点带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}反对暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然对那种对人畜无害的男士施暴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人畜无害？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是再胡来 我可就叫警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得我有你这样的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 真是个有趣的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想提醒那位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔垃圾要好好扔到垃圾桶里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们组是负责监督这个地区保洁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}城市清洁靠大家 花丸商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 话说回来 这位大姐我很中意你的魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被前辈救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟学生时代没有任何区别嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比学生时代更稳重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以前的阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那种人找茬的话可是会吓哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为什么前辈会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么精力充沛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈救了阿土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟着她们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有穿帮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是约好下周一起去喝酒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恋爱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有中意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全没有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比起这个 工作方面还没有完全适应…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喝酒的话随时都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来和女孩子约好一起去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有事再打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果那个人因为恋爱了改去约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你也是 有事就打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他还那么高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中意的人是指杏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周日的安排没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会人的休息日就是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师看上去好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 柊 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土本打算去约会的 但是被甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？被甩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？哭了吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才跟踪我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很担心你有没有三心二意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个要吃鲷鱼烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天我发现了一家很好吃的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲷鱼烧？！要吃要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲷鱼烧从头到尾都装满了豆沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探团行动结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是有点担心阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏呢 就是阿土站着看H书也不会在意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算阿土看着女服务员流口水也会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 连那种样子都看到了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你们看到很糗的样子了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 倒 翁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来探讨未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 跳得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏要有个带庭院的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小杏等等 小梅也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要养一只小狗 生很多很多孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 小冬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君 我们快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在走廊里跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 抱歉把你丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅摔倒了 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男孩子帮助了小梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像叫佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在做什么？师父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佑 大悟和阳翔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤治君 你认识他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们都是向日葵班的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过师父 您叫我贤治君太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接叫我贤治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把从老师和其他学生那里得来的情报汇总了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是小早川佑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵中班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里一共4口人 为长男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血型是O
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的食物是汉堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中班吗 跟阿土比起来还是个小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是阿土比较帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君也很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到佑君胸口就会难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到他的眼睛就会心跳加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是恋爱啊 去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏每天都在向阿土告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小杏 果然是够牵强的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也许正如小杏所说的那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定明天佑君就搬家了（再见 拜拜）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定明天佑君会被外星人拐走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许明天second impact就会来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还会爆发伊修瓦尔战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 说过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对 小梅要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好向佑君道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 能不能做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像杏一样每天磨练女人味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能水到渠成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人味？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨练？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天护理皮肤不能偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是面对镜子练习微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是洗澡的时候要按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身浴也是很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再不出来小心泡晕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够 为了阿土我一定要变漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么漂亮可爱的杏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土却在乎世人的眼光不把杏当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果面对面说话害羞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就写信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏也要写
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接把你感谢的心意写上去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给阿土看我写给他的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谢谢」怎么写…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅不会写…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说佑君也有可能不会读
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅果然还是不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 问题在于年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 阿土给我花束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅的情书怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信也许太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说长长的话如果太难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说两句道谢的话或者送礼物怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物的话 就送小梅想送的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有女孩子在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的小班生 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃球…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起捡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君 干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直心跳不已 没能和佑君说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是恋爱呀 酸酸甜甜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把佑君单独叫出来 就不会紧张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅只需要等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这样比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧！在校园的一角告白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛也是很重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去叫佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 总觉得很兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏和小冬为了小梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就要好好向佑君说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！接下来就来想想告白的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白的台词？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏知道一句秘藏的台词哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样佑君也会对你神魂颠倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么？商量恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是恶作剧 是在商量小梅的告白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白？小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 说漏嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然杏经常胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是小梅的话还真有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您百忙之中来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫小梅吧？找我有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小梅加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要对你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 就是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说她就是这样向爸爸告白的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说有刚才那句话就足够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑君 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好一起到外面去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好 稍等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君为了小梅推迟了跟朋友的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 佑君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你刚才帮了小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅想要跟佑君道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 好好道谢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 一起去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回土田老师的妹妹真弓姐姐会来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有游泳池的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}花丸游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}花丸作战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}花丸哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}花丸住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さわったらね　だめだっていうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:23.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かたまらなくて、いたい　雨あがりのハート
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:28.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみが揺らした恋の　真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水の　冠って、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:36.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すてきなもの　おとしてくから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:41.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面張力　あふれだすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:48.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オモチャ箱の夢たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:52.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:58.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いかけて　転んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひっしだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:06.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの日も今も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:15.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わらって　つかめるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来は　その手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:25.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽根のように　舞い降りる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.24,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不能碰这碰那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:23.81,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么死板 放晴的心情 有点失落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:28.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因你摇晃的恋爱的正中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.20,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溅起了如皇冠般的水花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:36.39,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的东西 总是会逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:41.19,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面张力 洋溢出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:48.65,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具箱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:52.99,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:58.21,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力追赶 即使摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.42,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:06.69,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:15.05,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑吧 我们能把握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.46,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那宛如羽毛般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:25.94,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘落的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【STAFF】
